General.Name: Atomo Diagnostics Ltd
General.Description: Atomo Diagnostics Limited engages in the development and sale of medical devices worldwide. It offers rapid diagnostic test devices for HIV screening, pregnancy test, and respiratory test. Atomo Diagnostics Limited was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Leichhardt, Australia.
